Installation
1. Install a web server like apache, LightHTTPd, ngix or any other whith
PHP(5.3 or newer).
2. Enable SQLite support in your PHP installation.
3. Copy Stream-Planner directory to /var/www, ~/public_html on any other
directory where you are storing your web files.
4. Create /usr/local/stream_planner/ directory and make in readable and
writeable for your www server or modify config.php file and change
database storing directory.
5. Edit config.php file and choose language of application: pl_PL or en_US.
5. Type in your browser http://localhost/directory/to/the/stream/planner.
6. Organize your time.




